name: Adventure Explorer Walkie-Talkies
detailDescription: Embark on exciting adventures with the Adventure Explorer Walkie-Talkies. This set of two toy phones allows kids to communicate with each other from a distance. They feature a durable design, a built-in microphone, and a speaker for clear communication. Perfect for outdoor play and imaginative missions.

name: Circuit Genius
detailDescription: Circuit Genius is an educational electronic kit that teaches kids about circuits and electronics through hands-on experiments. It includes various components and a detailed instruction manual.

name: MiniTech Smartphone
detailDescription: The MiniTech Smartphone is a realistic imitation phone for kids. It features a touch screen, colorful icons, and sound effects. Children can pretend to make calls, send messages, and take pictures with the built-in camera. The toy phone helps develop imagination and role-playing skills. Batteries included.

name: DroneX
detailDescription: DroneX is a high-performance drone with a built-in camera. It features intelligent flight modes, a stable flight control system, and real-time video transmission.

name: MicroSquad
detailDescription: MicroSquad is a set of mini robots that can be programmed to perform coordinated tasks. They communicate wirelessly and can be controlled using a smartphone or tablet.

name: Circuit Explorer
detailDescription: Circuit Explorer is an electronic kit that introduces kids to the world of circuits and electricity. It includes various components and a fun activity guide.

name: Super Speed Racer
detailDescription: The Super Speed Racer is a high-performance remote control car designed for racing enthusiasts. It features a sleek design, powerful motor, and responsive controls. Race against your friends or set new lap records on your own. Suitable for both indoor and outdoor use. Batteries included.

name: Transforming Robot Car
detailDescription: The Transforming Robot Car is a versatile toy that can be enjoyed as both a car and a robot. Watch as it seamlessly transforms between the two modes with the push of a button. It features flashing lights, sound effects, and a remote control for easy operation. Requires 4 AA batteries (not included).

name: Off-Road Adventure Truck
detailDescription: Take your playtime off-road with the Off-Road Adventure Truck. This rugged vehicle can conquer any terrain with its large wheels and suspension system. The truck comes with a rechargeable battery and a remote control for easy maneuverability. It also features working headlights and realistic engine sounds.

name: SmartKids Learning Phone
detailDescription: The SmartKids Learning Phone is a fun and educational toy designed for young children. It features a vibrant touch screen, interactive buttons, and various learning activities. Kids can learn numbers, letters, animals, and play games while developing their cognitive skills. The toy phone requires 3 AAA batteries (included).

name: RoboBot
detailDescription: RoboBot is a programmable robot that can perform various tasks and interact with its environment. It comes with a user-friendly interface and can be controlled using a mobile app.

name: Drift King Racer
detailDescription: Experience the thrill of drifting with the Drift King Racer. This remote control car is designed for impressive sideways slides and precise control. It features a lightweight yet durable frame, adjustable suspension, and high-grip tires. The car comes with a rechargeable battery and a responsive remote control.

name: Music & Play Toy Phone
detailDescription: The Music & Play Toy Phone is a delightful musical toy for toddlers. It features colorful buttons that play different melodies, animal sounds, and teach numbers. The toy phone has a sturdy construction and is designed to withstand rough play. It promotes fine motor skills, auditory development, and imaginative play.
